&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/CHICAGO-SHAY-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-8362&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/CHICAGO-SHAY-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;CHICAGO- SHAY- OFFER- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;100&quot; height=&quot;60&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;Located in the River North area of Chicago, Shay is an upscale club with a state-of-the-art sound system playing Top 40&amp;#8217;s, Hip Hop and popular music by DJs that keep a chic crowd moving. The open floorplan is sleekly elegant with curved lines and light palette. Two raised VIP areas and a DJ booth surrounding the bar and dancefloor makes the perfect setting to enjoy creative cocktails or bottle service along with a small bites menu.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please visit&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.SHAYchicago.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;SHAY&amp;#8217;s website&lt;/a&gt;,&nbsp;contact SHAY by phone at +1-312-654-1230&nbsp;or email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:info@SHAYchicago.com&quot;&gt;info@SHAYchicago.com&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Nightlife Access to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, the date you would like to attend, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel)&nbsp;phone number and email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Please contact the nightclub by phone or email 24 hours prior to your arrival date to reconfirm. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Nightlife Access If not reconfirmed your reservation may be given away if the need arises&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ages 21 &amp;amp; Over. ID must be provided.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Benefit is applicable for up to 4 guests in total.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dress code will be strictly enforced. Management reserves the right to refuse entry to guests due to visible intoxication, lack of proper ID, failure to adhere to dress code, or capacity limits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access is granted only with reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Late arrivals past midnight will be required to pay any required cover charges, despite having a reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Nightlife&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Diners Club Card must be used for payment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Nightlife Access benefit may not be combined with other offers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Nightclub/Lounge merchant.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reservations&nbsp;based on availability at the time of booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nightclub/lounge participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Blackout dates may apply due to event buyouts. Special event/DJs may incur a charge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

